# AI Reflection

## 1. How Did You Use AI in This Assignment?

I used AI as a learning and support tool throughout this assignment. 
It helped me better understand the project requirements, organize my development process, and plan the implementation of the different features. 
AI also assisted me in identifying and fixing coding errors, explaining SwiftUI concepts, exploring alternative solutions, and improving the overall quality and structure of my code. 
While AI provided guidance and suggestions, I was responsible for implementing, testing, and integrating all of the features into my application.

## 2. What Did AI Help You Learn?

AI helped me better understand several SwiftUI concepts, including building a login screen, using `SecureField`, implementing password visibility toggles, validating user input, and storing data with `@AppStorage`. 
It also helped me learn best practices for creating a more user-friendly and maintainable application.

## 3. What Did You Do Yourself?

I designed and implemented all the required features, integrated them into the existing application, tested their functionality, fixed bugs, and ensured that the final project met the assignment requirements. 
I also documented the additional features in the README and prepared the project for submission.

